{"tid":49684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以幫我解夢?","createTime":"2016-12-22T01:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T06:37:30.000Z","uid":48042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"464052f2071f0b4ba0de01d124a200aac0f2d328","tid":49684,"uid":48042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:29:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今朝發左個好長嘅夢<br />\n我有啲唔記得 大概個內容係<br />\n話說個情境係我聽緊歌散步<br />\n係類似商場嘅地方到遊蕩<br />\n突然有條友衝埋嚟搶左我個headphone<br />\n我當然想去繼續追 但比人拉住左隻手<br />\n嗰個人係我暗戀左好幾年嘅女仔(以下代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同我講 : 唔好追 救我呀<br />\n望後見到成群蒙面人拎住又刀又剩追上嚟<br />\n我自然反應捉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻手 不過係手腕 <br />\n走到咁上下 走到去一個商場電梯位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />甩開左我 同我講 : Sorry呀 我......<br />\n話都未講完 蒙面人已經追上 仲包圍住我地<br />\n我諗抱住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由電梯跳落去嘅時候<br />\n蒙面人s突然放低刀 除左個面罩 <br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部都係我啲朋友呀 同學呀<br />\n中學同學 以前教會識嘅  網友都有<br />\n佢地係咁同我講 : 放棄佢啦 冇可能㗎你地<br />\n正當我想開口嘅時候 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搶先一步答 : 好<br />\n佢地聽完就同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬧交 詳細我唔係好記得<br />\n鬧完佢地起勢咁追我 好似喪屍咁<br />\n人群之中已經唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後好似老師呀 屋企人呀 親戚都加入埋<br />\n走頭無路嘅我走到上天台 <br />\n有班大專既同學係天台門口叫我出去<br />\n佢地係出面頂住<br />\n我就用野頂住唯一既出入口<br />\n我頓時腦一片空白 冇到門另一邊嘅聲音<br />\n訓左係天台 唱下歌 諗下有咩要做 就醒左<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫我解夢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次個夢好長 亦都好深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能1999 仲好九唔搭八 <br />\n可以當文筆差嘅故睇左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e09f2cc889366fa28b81364cd9c17d1dc67c35","tid":49684,"uid":48042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df038c29f003bb9c81d469472758eafca4698cf","tid":49684,"uid":48042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}